    <title>AI开发实战训练营 - 课程大纲</title>
    <style>
        /* @font-face removed to fix xhtml2pdf compatibility */
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'SimSun', Arial, sans-serif !important;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
